doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    title Verify Your Email - Salumi Tracker
    style.
      body {
        background-color: #f9f5f0;
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        color: #5a3e36;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .container {
        background: #fff7ef;
        border: 1px solid #e0d4c0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .button {
        display: block;
        width: fit-content;
        background-color: #b2613c;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 2rem auto 1rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #a48d7c;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

  body
    .container
      h1 Welcome to Salumi Tracker!
      p Hello #{firstName},
      p
        | Thank you for signing up for 
        strong Salumi Tracker
        | — your personal assistant for managing artisan-cured meats.
      p Please verify your email to activate your account and begin tracking your batches.
      a.button(href=verificationUrl) Verify Your Email
      p If the button doesn’t work, you can copy and paste the link below into your browser:
      p
        | #{url}
      .footer
        | You're receiving this email because you created an account at Salumi Tracker.
        br
        | If this wasn't you, feel free to ignore it.
